			<div class="content" id="post-content-4836449">
									

<p>Thank you so much for the feedback! I really do appreciate the reality check!</p>
<p>I have worked on the concept hoping and waiting to be greenlit, but the legality and licensing of it came into question, so I was trying to get some of it ironed out before continuing. but it has since kind of gotten further out of hand than i had originally intended at this point.</p>
<p>I do plan on starting the twitch channel either way, but in trying to come up with an interesting character for that, i loved the idea of tying it into one of my favorite universe (SCP). Yet so far i have mostly received backlash from the licensing team and others. maybe it won't work after all, but i would still like to test the waters a little deeper before i draw that conclusion.</p>

